title: VOTE VOTE VOTE!
itunes:title: VOTE VOTE VOTE!
description:
Friday 11/2- Today on the show Charlamagne, Angela record and our political pundit Angela Rye recorded live in Miami to help encourage people to vote . Also, they were joined by Mayor and hopefully future Governor of Florida Andrew Gillum, President of Florida Rights Restoration Coalition Desmond Meade and spokesperson Sybrina Fulton to help inform people about the importance of voting.
